query.name: seller_warehouse_code
query.description: Seller warehouse code. Default value is seller's first sellerWarehouse, usually it's seller's address in asc. You can get the warehouse list by openApi listIcpWarehouse.

query.name: estimate_time
query.description: Estimated Time in UTC+0. format is "yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ".

query.name: inventory_type
query.description: Inventory type, 1 for good, 101 for defective.

query.name: skus
query.description: List of outbound skus. Max list size is 100.

common.name: app_key
common.description: Unique app ID issued by LAZADA Open Platform console when you apply for an app category

common.name: timestamp
common.description: The time stamp of the request e.g. 1517820392000 (which translates to 5 February 2018 08:46:32) with less than 7200s difference from UTC time

common.name: sign_method
common.description: The HMAC hash algorithm you are using to calculate your signature
